<li><a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2024/05/06/iphone-17-slim-to-feature-6-55-inch-display/">6.6-inch OLED display</a> with Face ID <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2024/07/24/kuo-ultra-thin-iphone-17-specs/">and a Dynamic Island</a></li><br/>
